code: const API_URL='http://localhost:8080';export const getContainers=async()=>{const response=await fetch("".concat(API_URL,"/containers"));return response.json();};export const createContainer=async config=>{const response=await fetch("".concat(API_URL,"/containers"),{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify(config)});return response.text();};export const executeContainer=async id=>{const response=await fetch("".concat(API_URL,"/containers/").concat(id,"/execute"),{method:'POST'});return response.text();};
